            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Professional Referrals</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Systematic nurturing of financial advisors, accountants, and insurance agents.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Value-add content</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Referral tracking</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Appreciation touches</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-cyan-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Update Reminders</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Automated annual reviews and life-event update prompts.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Annual check-ins</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Life event triggers</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Law change alerts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-cyan-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Educational Nurturing</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Automated content explaining trusts, powers of attorney, and planning strategies.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Concept explainers</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Tasteful messaging</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Trust building</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-green-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-emerald-400 mb-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
